  "title": "Mulesoft Integration Architect (Mulesoft Certified Developer L1 / Mule 4)",
  "description": "<p>Experience:</p><ul><li><u>8+ years hands-on with MuleSoft (Mule 4, Anypoint Platform) across at least 2–3 end-to-end projects.</u></li></ul><p>Certifications:</p><ul><li><u>Required: MuleSoft Certified Developer – Level 1 (Mule 4)</u></li><li>Strongly preferred: MuleSoft Certified Integration Architect – Level 1</li><li>Nice-to-have: MuleSoft Certified Platform Architect – Level 1 and 1 cloud provider certification.</li></ul><p>Skills:</p><ul><li>API-led connectivity, RAML/OpenAPI, strong DataWeave 2.x.</li><li>Anypoint Platform (Design Center, API Manager, Runtime Manager, Exchange).</li><li>CloudHub/RTF deployment, security policies, logging/monitoring, and CI/CD with Maven/Git.</li><li>Proven delivery on complex integrations, ideally including Salesforce or a major enterprise platform.</li></ul><p>Ways of working:</p><ul><li>Lead client conversation on overall integration architecture for Salesforce platform. </li><li>Leads technical design, performs code reviews, coaches junior developers, and works within agile teams.</li></ul>",
